<hw>pachyderma</hw> <pr>(p⟦acr⟧k"⟦icr⟧*d⟦etil⟧r"m⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An abnormal thickening of the skin
